 be upon him, said, \u201cA woman should not fast in the presence of her husband except with his permission.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 4820, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1026 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim Al-Nawawi said, \u201cThe reason for\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6663,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/19\/grand-petty-theft\/","url_meta":{"origin":9874,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Thieves: Cutting the hand applied to grand theft, not petty theft","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 19, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The hand of the thief was never cut in the lifetime of the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, for what is less than the price of a shield or piece of armor, and both of them were expensive. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6408, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3213,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/05\/16\/no-talking-jumuah-khutbah\/","url_meta":{"origin":9874,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Khutbah: Not allowed to speak during Friday Sermon","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 16, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \